<HEAD>Some Charges Dropped in Killing of Two Americans</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MEXICO CITY (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A panel of judges in Jalisco state dropped
kidnapping and secret burial charges against five Mexicans in
connection with the slaying of two Americans, but they are still
